description: Tanik trees line this winding path, the forest floor littered with browning pinecones full of seed.  Dappled moonlight breaking through the twisting branches settles in patches here and there.  A small creek trickles out from an underground seep, running clear over multi-hued stones that almost look like dusky jewels.
